      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the summary, but it's a bit too brief to be a full memo. A partner is going to want to see how these concepts actually interact in a real-world workflow.\n\nCan you expand this into a more formal, multi-paragraph memo? I need you to go into more detail on the obligations of the controller vs the processor, and explicitly detail the rights of the data subjects. \n\nJust a reminder: the audit tool is still going to be running on this version. I know I said not to just stuff it, but please make sure every single one of those 20 terms is included and well-represented in the expanded text. I really need this to look thorough so the automated score doesn't flag it for missing documentation.",
